          {
            "speaker-npc-id": -1,
            "text": {
              "english": "Hello there. Is there something I could help you with today?"
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": 4,
            "text": {
              "english": "Good day! Yes, I think I have something interesting you could help me with."
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": 4,
            "text": {
              "english": "About two days ago I heard some weird screaming coming from another village down the road."
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": 4,
            "text": {
              "english": "I thought it was nothing, until I heard my son tell me about the church in that village being demolished."
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": -1,
            "text": {
              "english": "Hmm hmm. That sounds very strange. Would you like me to take a look?"
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": 4,
            "text": {
              "english": "I would highly appreciate it if you could have a look at the church."
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": 4,
            "text": {
              "english": "Come back to me as soon as you can with whatever information you got. Those screams were horrifying."
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": -1,
            "text": {
              "english": "I will go ahead and take a look at it."
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
