        "dialogue": [
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": -1,
            "text": {
              "english": "Wow. This is... indeed horrifying..."
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": -1,
            "text": {
              "english": "There is all blood and not a single soul to be heard or seen."
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": -1,
            "text": {
              "english": "I should go back to Richard and tell him there is something very wrong."
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "talk_with_npc",
      "data": {
        "npc-id": 4,
        "dialogue": [
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": 4,
            "text": {
              "english": "Good to see you again. Tell me. What did you see?"
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": -1,
            "text": {
              "english": "I would not recommend anyone to go there. The church was full of blood and skulls. I don't know what to say."
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": 4,
            "text": {
              "english": "Oh no. I have a slight feeling what is going on."
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": -1,
            "text": {
              "english": "What is it?"
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": 4,
            "text": {
              "english": "Lately I have heard rumours that there was a invasion of zombies around town and also the surrounding villages."
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": 4,
            "text": {
              "english": "The zombies must have gotten to the church first. Oh no..."
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": -1,
            "text": {
              "english": "Oh no?"
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": 4,
            "text": {
              "english": "We might be their prey this night!"
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": -1,
            "text": {
              "english": "What can I do to save you and all of the citizens?"
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": 4,
            "text": {
              "english": "Please. I beg you. Kill 15 zombies. That should be enough for us to prepare for more nights of zombies. For now. Kill 15 of them."
            }
          },
          {
            "speaker-npc-id": -1,
            "text": {
              "english": "Richard, you can count on me."
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
